<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/hazardtype/tsunami> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A seri es of waves (with lo ng wavele ngths when traveli ng across the deep ocean) that ar e generated by a di splacement of massive amounts of wat er throughunderwat er earthquakes, volc anic eruptions or landsli des. Tsunami waves travel at very high speed across the ocean but as they begi n to reach shallow water they slo w down and the wave grows steeper."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/hazardtype:1> .
