<https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/hazardtype/tsunami> <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "A series of waves, with long wavelengths when traveling across the deep ocean, that are generated by a displacement of massive amounts of water through under water-earthquakes, volcanic eruptions or landslides. Tsunami waves travel at very high speed across the ocean but as they begi n to reach shallow water they slo w down and the wave grows steeper."@en <https://registry.inspire.gv.at/codelist/hazardtype:1> .
